data.description:
Spacious and updated home located in the peaceful neighborhood of Robinwood. This stunning property features a large open floor plan, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. New LVP flooring and paint throughout. The kitchen is fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, and plenty of storage space. The master suite is complete with a walk-in closet with three additional bedrooms and recently updated bathrooms. Outside, the backyard offers a large patio area with an in-ground, completely renovated pool: new copping, liner, plumbing, saltwater system, and cleaning equipment which all comes with warranty.

Seller is offering $8500 towards a 2-1 Buydown or Closing Costs AND a home warranty with Home Warranty of America (up to $585).
